    "description": "在这款复古运动主题的Roguelike第一人称射击游戏中挥击、投掷、踢飞或猛砸各种圆球并横扫怪物大军，被吸入一个神秘传送门后，你发现自己获得了将各式运动器械改造成致命武器的能力。<br><br>- 使用各式运动器械打败来自50年代怪兽电影的怪物大军，发射尖刺棒球、注入闪电的冰球、爆炸性高尔夫球、利刃保龄球等等  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146440/extras/e452ac1e788e7c9b7981121a4eedd990.poster.avif?t=1772221987\" width=780 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146440/extras/e452ac1e788e7c9b7981121a4eedd990.webm?t=1772221987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146440/extras/e452ac1e788e7c9b7981121a4eedd990.mp4?t=1772221987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 你走进了自己最喜欢的商场影院，但是一觉醒来，你却发现自己来到了一个奇幻世界，充斥着原本只存在于赛珞璐胶片上的各种可怕怪物。你必须想法设法弄清楚这到底是怎么回事。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146440/extras/5e689ccf71210ef4b818fde97338dd95.poster.avif?t=1772221987\" width=780 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146440/extras/5e689ccf71210ef4b818fde97338dd95.webm?t=1772221987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146440/extras/5e689ccf71210ef4b818fde97338dd95.mp4?t=1772221987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 拾取并升级数量众多的运动器械、华丽套装与强大特性，尝试组合不同的装置道具，并找到最强大的配置来横扫怪物大军。也许终有一天，你能够找到回家的路 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146440/extras/b765ddf0ef97d0817acfad25891a5922.poster.avif?t=1772221987\" width=780 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146440/extras/b765ddf0ef97d0817acfad25891a5922.webm?t=1772221987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146440/extras/b765ddf0ef97d0817acfad25891a5922.mp4?t=1772221987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色：</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>使用各式各样的运动器材去屠杀怪物！ <br></li><li>6种B级片主题的地形环境与数十块战斗区域<br></li><li>家喻户晓的银幕怪物们将对你发起无情追杀 <br></li><li>每种运动武器都拥有十余种升级<br></li><li>连击、秘密、花式射击以及更多！！ <br></li><li>忠实还原50年代氛围的复古像素风格</li></ul>",
